        <h2>How to Save Money on Utilities</h2>
        <p><strong>Published on:</strong> January 5, 2025</p>
        <p>Utility bills can add up quickly, but you can reduce your costs by making a few adjustments. Here are some tips:</p>
        <h3>1. Use Energy-Efficient Appliances</h3>
        <p>Look for appliances with an ENERGY STAR rating to save on electricity.</p>
        <h3>2. Turn Off Lights and Electronics</h3>
        <p>Switch off lights and unplug devices when not in use.</p>
        <h3>3. Conserve Water</h3>
        <p>Fix leaks and install low-flow showerheads to save water and reduce costs.</p>
